OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine end
OL,6,Fto the day, with some prolonged
OL,7,Fevening sunshine. Staying dry with
OL,8,Flong clear spells and turning chilly,
OL,9,Fwith a touch of ground frost in
OL,10,Fsheltered spots. Winds mostly light
OL,11,Fbut becoming breezier along coasts and
OL,12,Fover hills.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTuesday:FDry, fine and warm, the
OL,15,Fsunshine perhaps turning hazier later.
OL,16,FA brisk breeze, especially across
OL,17,Fhills and along the coast, giving a
OL,18,Fnoticeably cooler feel here.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
