OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FMostly
OL,6,Fdry Wednesday, generally cloudier
OL,7,Falthough still with warm bright or
OL,8,Fsunny spells. Lighter winds. Thursday
OL,9,Fcolder, breezy with sunshine and
OL,10,Fshowers. Friday, cloud, rain and
OL,11,Fstronger winds moving east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
